connected, remains energetically

00:08:18.660 --> 00:08:23.850 align:middle line:84%
connected, even when the space
that separates the matter

00:08:23.850 --> 00:08:24.990 align:middle line:90%
is of great distance.

00:08:24.990 --> 00:08:27.250 align:middle line:84%
In this case, it was
measured in miles.

00:08:27.250 --> 00:08:32.100 align:middle line:84%
So now, scientists took this
understanding, this discovery,

00:08:32.100 --> 00:08:35.400 align:middle line:84%
and they began to
look into the universe

00:08:35.400 --> 00:08:38.970 align:middle line:84%
and see where else this
entanglement might apply.

00:08:38.970 --> 00:08:41.250 align:middle line:84%
And what they found is
that, not only does it

00:08:41.250 --> 00:08:47.520 align:middle line:84%
apply on distances as small
as 14 miles, what they found

00:08:47.520 --> 00:08:51.510 align:middle line:84%
is that galaxies on one
side of the universe

00:08:51.510 --> 00:08:54.450 align:middle line:84%
