universe, light years distant.

00:08:58.619 --> 00:08:59.910 align:middle line:90%
And they said, how can this be?

00:08:59.910 --> 00:09:01.980 align:middle line:90%
How can this be possible?

00:09:01.980 --> 00:09:03.900 align:middle line:84%
